<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8" />
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
        <title>문의하기 - 마법연구회</title>

        <link
            href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined"
            rel="stylesheet"
        />

        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/component/style/base.css" />
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/component/style/badges.css" />
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/component/style/buttons.css" />
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/component/style/forms.css" />
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/user/mypage.css" />
    </head>
    <body>
        <script>
            (function() {
                const savedTheme = localStorage.getItem('theme') || 'light';
                document.documentElement.setAttribute('data-theme', savedTheme);
            })();
        </script>
        <div id="root">
            <%- include('../partials/header') %>

            <main class="main-content">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="mypage-header">
                        <h1 class="title">문의하기</h1>
                    </div>

                    <div class="contact-section">
                        <div class="contact-info">
                            <div class="contact-item">
                                <div class="contact-icon">
                                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined">mail</span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="contact-content">
                                    <h3>이메일 문의</h3>
                                    <p>일반적인 문의사항이나 제안사항은 이메일로 보내주세요.</p>
                                    <a href="mailto:support@magicresearch.com" class="contact-link">support@magicresearch.com</a>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="contact-item">
                                <div class="contact-icon">
                                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined">bug_report</span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="contact-content">
                                    <h3>버그 신고</h3>
                                    <p>기술적인 문제나 버그는 전용 페이지를 통해 신고해주세요.</p>
                                    <a href="/feedback" class="contact-link">버그 신고하기</a>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="contact-item">
                                <div class="contact-icon">
                                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined">code</span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="contact-content">
                                    <h3>개발자 문의</h3>
                                    <p>GitHub를 통해 개발자와 직접 소통하실 수 있습니다.</p>
                                    <a href="https://github.com/Tafka-4/MRSPlayground" class="contact-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub Repository</a>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="contact-item">
                                <div class="contact-icon">
                                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined">schedule</span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="contact-content">
                                    <h3>응답 시간</h3>
                                    <p>문의사항에 대한 답변은 보통 24-48시간 내에 드립니다.</p>
                                    <span class="contact-text">평일 기준 1-2일</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="contact-form-container">
                            <h3>직접 문의하기</h3>
                            <form class="contact-form" id="contactForm">
                                <div class="form-group">
                                    <label for="subject">제목</label>
                                    <input type="text" id="subject" name="subject" required placeholder="문의 제목을 입력해주세요">
                                </div>

                                <div class="form-group">
                                    <label for="category">카테고리</label>
                                    <select id="category" name="category" required>
                                        <option value="">카테고리를 선택해주세요</option>
                                        <option value="general">일반 문의</option>
                                        <option value="technical">기술적 문제</option>
                                        <option value="feature">기능 요청</option>
                                        <option value="account">계정 관련</option>
                                        <option value="other">기타</option>
                                    </select>
                                </div>

                                <div class="form-group">
                                    <label for="email">이메일</label>
                                    <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required placeholder="답변을 받을 이메일 주소를 입력해주세요">
                                </div>

                                <div class="form-group">
                                    <label for="message">문의 내용</label>
                                    <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="8" required placeholder="문의 내용을 자세히 적어주세요. 문제 상황을 구체적으로 설명해주시면 더 정확한 답변을 드릴 수 있습니다."></textarea>
                                </div>

                                <div class="form-actions">
                                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">
                                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined">send</span>
                                        문의 보내기
                                    </button>
                                </div>
                            </form>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </main>
        </div>
        <%- include('../partials/footer') %>

        <style>
            .container {
                max-width: 1200px !important;
                width: 95% !important;
            }

            .contact-section {
                display: grid;
                grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
                gap: 3rem;
                margin-top: 1rem;
            }

            .contact-info {
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 1.5rem;
            }

            .contact-item {
                display: flex;
                gap: 1rem;
                padding: 1.5rem;
                background: var(--card-background);
                border-radius: 1rem;
                box-shadow: var(--shadow);
                transition: all 0.2s ease;
            }

            .contact-item:hover {
                transform: translateY(-2px);
                box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            }

            [data-theme='dark'] .contact-item:hover {
                box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            }

            [data-theme='dark'] .contact-icon {
                background: #8b5cf6;
            }

            .contact-icon {
                flex-shrink: 0;
                width: 48px;
                height: 48px;
                background: var(--primary-color);
                border-radius: 0.75rem;
                display: flex;
                align-items: center;
                justify-content: center;
                color: white;
            }

            .contact-icon .material-symbols-outlined {
                font-size: 1.5rem;
            }

            .contact-content h3 {
                color: var(--text-primary);
                font-size: 1.1rem;
                font-weight: 500;
                margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
            }

            .contact-content p {
                color: var(--text-secondary);
                line-height: 1.6;
                margin: 0 0 0.75rem 0;
                font-size: 0.9rem;
            }

            .contact-link {
                color: var(--primary-color);
                text-decoration: none;
                font-weight: 500;
                display: inline-flex;
                align-items: center;
                gap: 0.25rem;
            }

            .contact-link:hover {
                text-decoration: underline;
            }

            .contact-text {
                color: var(--text-primary);
                font-weight: 500;
            }

            .contact-form-container {
                background: var(--card-background);
                border-radius: 1rem;
                padding: 2rem;
                box-shadow: var(--shadow);
                height: fit-content;
            }

            .contact-form-container h3 {
                color: var(--text-primary);
                font-size: 1.3rem;
                font-weight: 500;
                margin: 0 0 1.5rem 0;
                border-bottom: 2px solid var(--primary-color);
                padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
            }

            .contact-form {
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 1.5rem;
            }

            .form-group {
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 0.5rem;
            }

            .form-group label {
                color: var(--text-primary);
                font-weight: 500;
                font-size: 0.9rem;
            }

            .form-group input,
            .form-group select,
            .form-group textarea {
                padding: 0.75rem;
                border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
                border-radius: 0.5rem;
                background: var(--background-color);
                color: var(--text-primary);
                font-size: 0.9rem;
                transition: border-color 0.2s ease;
            }

            .form-group input:focus,
            .form-group select:focus,
            .form-group textarea:focus {
                outline: none;
                border-color: var(--primary-color);
            }

            .form-group textarea {
                resize: vertical;
                min-height: 120px;
            }

            .form-actions {
                display: flex;
                justify-content: flex-end;
                margin-top: 1rem;
            }

            .btn {
                display: inline-flex;
                align-items: center;
                gap: 0.5rem;
                padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
                border: none;
                border-radius: 0.5rem;
                font-weight: 500;
                cursor: pointer;
                transition: all 0.2s ease;
                text-decoration: none;
            }

            .btn-primary {
                background: var(--primary-color);
                color: white;
            }

            .btn-primary:hover {
                background: var(--primary-hover);
                transform: translateY(-1px);
            }

            @media (max-width: 1024px) {
                .contact-section {
                    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                    gap: 2rem;
                }
            }

            @media (max-width: 768px) {
                .contact-item {
                    padding: 1rem;
                }

                .contact-icon {
                    width: 40px;
                    height: 40px;
                }

                .contact-icon .material-symbols-outlined {
                    font-size: 1.25rem;
                }

                .contact-form-container {
                    padding: 1.5rem;
                }
            }
        </style>

        <script>
            document.getElementById('contactForm').addEventListener('submit', function(e) {
                e.preventDefault();
                
                // 여기서 실제로는 서버로 데이터를 전송해야 함
                // 현재는 데모용으로 알림만 표시
                alert('문의가 접수되었습니다. 빠른 시일 내에 답변드리겠습니다.');
                
                // 폼 초기화
                this.reset();
            });
        </script>
    </body>
</html> 